{"tid":1309172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有中銀戶口請入,有你著數, 中銀卡可以去所有銀通 (Jetco) 機提款,勁方便!","createTime":"2019-07-12T05:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T15:33:29.000Z","uid":58307,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"04ef46213adf422a6114255031c775a4d7c83c12","tid":1309172,"uid":58307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:56:15.000Z","msg":"你用<span style=\"color: red;\">中銀卡</span>可以去所有 <span style=\"color: red;\">銀通 (Jetco) ATM機</span>(EG:東亞,星展,創興之類..)提款, 總之係 銀通 (Jetco) ATM機就得, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每一次係非中銀機提款 中銀都要付出$5 成本! </span></span></strong><br />\n每次扲幾百蚊,咁上下扲晒咪再用 轉數快&ndash; FPS 轉返幾百蚊落中銀, 之後又可以再去提款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以唔駛取消戶口, 留一千蚊係戶口, 依家又唔駛最低存款收費.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你諗下每日都有萬幾人咁做, 一個月中銀就多左百幾萬成本, 好過你就咁取消戶口(佢無成本) 仲有MPF 多要轉走呀, 中銀MPF收費好撚貴表現又廢!仲要D組合係多數買番支那公司!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06438ce0094f1033a919cb90b048a1d8c5f35c2","tid":1309172,"uid":263326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T05:58:55.000Z","msg":"冇呢D垃圾卡。但幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2acb351bc3606c131631dffce08764e32e9278fb","tid":1309172,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:01:10.000Z","msg":"冇支那卡，但照推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb697e8b9d7f81cdd1f360de058799bc457c0b3a","tid":1309172,"uid":58307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:01:11.000Z","msg":"推佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e5eb040f1b92e7765674b917f80c32c1895397","tid":1309172,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy